## Import

In Terraform v1.5.0 and later, use an import block to import apono_space using the Apono space identifier. For example:

```terraform
import {
  to = apono_space.production
  id = "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000"
}
```

Or via CLI:

```shell
terraform import apono_space.production 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
```
